- Rename  threads => tasks


- Default parameters
    Web app
      1 tasks, 512 KB
    Mobile
      2 tasks, 8 MB
    Local login
      4 tasks, 16 MB
    High-security key derivation 
    (PGP, password mgr, SSH, file encryption): 
      4 tasks, 128 MB
    

- API format (default for different deployment scenarios)



